^IBA(364.92,46,10,1,0)="This activity code first sets field (#.31) EXEMPT FROM SC to 'Yes' so the "
^IBA(364.92,46,10,2,0)="Resubmit process will consider this encounter as billable even though "
^IBA(364.92,46,10,3,0)="the patient is set up as service connected."
^IBA(364.92,46,10,4,0)="  "
^IBA(364.92,46,10,5,0)="It then automatically resubmits the encounter for autogeneration."
