^IBA(364.92,47,10,0)="^^4^4^3250414^"
^IBA(364.92,47,10,1,0)="When a user chooses the RS Review Status action and changes the status of"
^IBA(364.92,47,10,2,0)="an encounter entry, they are allowed to enter a comment to explain their"
^IBA(364.92,47,10,3,0)="edit. Also a new entry is added to the previous activity multiple for"
^IBA(364.92,47,10,4,0)="historical purposes."
